data.title: Jerry Rubin press conference
data.meta_description: Jerry Rubin, wearing shorts and a T-shirt labeled Save the Humans, with a small band of supporters, holds a press conference on Venice Beach to show support for street vendors and entertainers. Photograph dated Oct. 27, 1988.
